  <chunk id="089acb4677633e0cf2d35fd728e686c8aa887bc0.c2" text="Ebola virus (EBOV), the species responsible for the deadliest epidemic [1, 2] . With over 11,000 deaths during the 2013-2016 outbreak in Western Africa and no antiviral drug approved, understanding the biology of this virus is essential to develop specific treatments.">
